beer.beer_description: Refreshing IPA using a combination of US, Oz and Kiwi hops plus some Gladfields toffee malt for a sweet mid section. Not too rich in maltiness, this IPA is designed to slake and punch at the same time. Extended stay in the brite tank creates a clean mouthfeel but don't fret. The alcohol and the bitterness of an IPA is most definitely there in abundance so expect a beer with bite.
